{
  "stem": "16792.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 384.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Sometimes beans, or sometimes something else in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And after that, we got the chicken.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Friday night, normally is-- is a preparation for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And, uh-- what we did-- Friday night, we still can have hot meals from our stove.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And, um-- and then after that, what we did every Friday, when I was a little bit older, the preparation which my mother made was for whole Saturdays.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And Saturdays, we-- we could not cook.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That what we did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We bring the food which is prepared for Saturday during the day-- we-- I bring the food to a bakery.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And the bakery put it in the oven, in the side of the oven, to have it warm.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I pick up for Saturday-- I was going to pick up the food hot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And always, we have got hot food for Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then that what we have got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we have got compote-- compote is dessert.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We have got different type of food, apples.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And this is the way we-- we passed through the holidays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Also, uh, when I was a little bit older, I-- my grandfather has got something problem with his eyes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My grandfather, Meyer Reifer, from the father's father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, uh, the-- the doctor send him to Czechoslovakia for operations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And twice, he was-- operation, they kill both eyes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was his eyes from this time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my grandfather was very religious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And eveyday in the morning, he is go-- was going to the mikvah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know what the mikvah means.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A mikvah is a ritual-- ritual spa.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a special house, spa house, which you go to wash yourself, or you dip in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I took my grandfather after that, when he didn't see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was his eyes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
